---
---
<section class="section about-strip" data-handshake style="margin-top: 1rem;">
  <div class="about-text">
    <div class="section-label">Who I Am</div>
    <h2 class="hs-heading">A student building<br><span class="gradient-text">in public</span></h2>
    <p>Hey! I'm Om Jhamvar — a 10th grader from India obsessed with two things: football (specifically the tactical brilliance of Arsenal) and the craft of building software.</p>
    <p>This site is where I document everything I learn, analyze, and create. No polish required — just honest work in progress.</p>
    <div class="about-tags">
      <span class="about-tag">⚽ Arsenal FC</span>
      <span class="about-tag">💻 Web Dev</span>
      <span class="about-tag">🐍 Python</span>
      <span class="about-tag">📊 Data Analysis</span>
      <span class="about-tag">🧠 Tactics</span>
      <span class="about-tag">🎨 Design</span>
      <span class="about-tag">📖 Continuous Learner</span>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top: 2rem;">
      <a href="/about" class="btn-ghost">Full story →</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="glass-card tilt-card" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(76,201,240,0.08), rgba(138,79,255,0.08)); border-color: rgba(76,201,240,0.2);">
    <div class="card-shine"></div>
    <div style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--accent-1); letter-spacing: 0.15em; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">QUICK FACTS</div>
    <div id="quick-facts">
      <div class="quick-fact">
        <span class="qf-icon">🏫</span>
        <div>
          <div class="qf-label">Grade</div>
          <div class="qf-value">10th Grade Student</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="quick-fact">
        <span class="qf-icon">❤️</span>
        <div>
          <div class="qf-label">Club</div>
          <div class="qf-value">Arsenal FC</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="quick-fact">
        <span class="qf-icon">🔭</span>
        <div>
          <div class="qf-label">Currently</div>
          <div class="qf-value">Learning & building daily</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="quick-fact">
        <span class="qf-icon">🎯</span>
        <div>
          <div class="qf-label">Goal</div>
          <div class="qf-value">Build things that matter</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-strip {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 3rem 0;
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .about-strip { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
  .about-text h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .about-text p {
    color: var(--muted-text);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .about-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }
  .about-tag {
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    background: var(--glass-bg);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--muted-text);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .about-tag:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent-1);
    color: var(--accent-1);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .gradient-text {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-1), var(--accent-2));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }
  .quick-fact {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .qf-icon { font-size: 1.2rem; }
  .qf-label { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--muted-text); text-transform: uppercase; }
  .qf-value { font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-strip { padding: 1.5rem 0 !important; gap: 1.5rem !important; }
  }
</style>